WEBVTT

1
00:05:10.630 --> 00:05:12.900 
我真的没有信心可以为我们的家庭
I just don't ever see us being able to provide

2
00:05:12.910 --> 00:05:16.370 
创造一个安全可靠的未来
a secure future for our family.

3
00:05:17.270 --> 00:05:19.820 
我们刚刚在星城警用电台上发现了可疑的内容
Hey. We just got some strange chatter over the SCPD scanner.

4
00:05:19.820 --> 00:05:21.450 
有人报警说在市区的
Someone called in a bomb threat

5
00:05:21.510 --> 00:05:23.050 
一个综合购物大楼里发现炸弹威胁
at a shopping complex downtown.

6
00:05:23.050 --> 00:05:25.640 
这个人利用了信号跳转技术  无法追踪号码
Somebody using a signal-bounced untraceable number.

7
00:05:25.640 --> 00:05:26.420 
很可疑
Suspicious.

8
00:05:26.420 --> 00:05:29.340 
为什么惠美子要给她自己的袭击进行预警
Why would Emiko give an advance warning on her own attack?

9
00:05:29.340 --> 00:05:30.400 
这说不通
It doesn't make sense.

10
00:05:30.400 --> 00:05:33.420 
这样整座大楼里的人都会被疏散到外面的广场
So that the whole complex will evacuate into the plaza outside,

11
00:05:33.420 --> 00:05:34.760 
外面的广场才是她打算使用天鹅座的地方
where she'll deploy the Cygnus.

12
00:05:34.760 --> 00:05:36.480 
这样才能让伤亡最大化
Maximizing the casualty count.

13
00:05:36.480 --> 00:05:38.290 
我们决不能让这种事发生
Well, we can't let that happen.

14
00:05:39.300 --> 00:05:40.720 
我们一定能阻止她  我们走
We won't. Let's move out.

